            "title": "<p>1500W Peak Motor</p>",
            "content": "<p>The F26 is equipped with a powerful 1500W motor that delivers responsive acceleration and dependable riding support. Whether you are commuting through the city, cruising through your neighborhood, or taking on light outdoor routes, the F26 gives you the power to ride with confidence.</p>",
